A4.text: The borough gained the area of the former urban districts of Gosforth and Newburn, and the parishes of Brunswick, Dinnington, Hazlerigg, North Gosforth and Woolsington.

A5.text: Outside the city centre, the largest suburban shopping areas are Gosforth and Byker.
